title: Total softwood and hardwood , stocks in Canada 2016
summary: The graph shows the hardwood of softwood in Canada over the year of 2016 .
The data is presented in cubic meters .
According to the graph hardwood of softwood is the highest in March and the lowest in December .
gold: Softwood and hardwood stock totals in Canada during each month of 2016 . The total rose from slightly over 72000 cubic meters in January to over 75000 cubic meters in April . It then experienced a drop to less than 68000 cubic meters from May to July , after which it continued to decline until reaching a minimum level in December of under 66000 cubic meters .
